{"tid":1299790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織香港分會：林鄭拒用「撤回」激化情勢","createTime":"2019-07-09T07:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:34:12.000Z","uid":212626,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bc1fc424916de865a2bf891079e734b103342a","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今天會見傳媒，宣布《逃犯條例》修訂草案已「壽終正寢」。國際特赦組織香港分會發表聲明，指林鄭月娥拒絕使用「撤回」的字眼，只會繼續激化香港現時的情況。<br />\n<br />\n組織指出，警方在6.12金鐘衝突中使用過分武力，違反國際法及國際準則，單靠監警會調查不足以得知真相，亦難挽回公眾信任。<br />\n<br />\n組織強調，當局須進行獨立、公正、有效及迅速的調查，而當日負責指揮的高級警務人員亦須面對司法調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2187016%2F&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1SEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=b810b690\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187016/</a>"},{"pid":"2af35ef87b3a3ecbaabec9da32d3a935f06bbc1a","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c11c82d3ca282864c3ee2ea1c76b6f3bbc2e22","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織確認香港警察違反國際人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1247785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1247785/page/1</a><br />\n同一個組織"},{"pid":"0edae0cc77002144e40c0b7d3cf751eafc34ea95","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae4f63065b7e99db8c32d70b27f43f34388e5e5","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79068a235112027073541f14eff9baf49af31719","tid":1299790,"uid":42139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"重申7大訴求：<br />\n 1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n 2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n 3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n 4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n 6. 承諾不推行社會信用評分制度<br />\n 7. 拆除所有監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n試著說監控燈柱, 不要說智慧燈柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802dd6969ecad5d155cbbaa8efecde9560f5650e","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381c05dccfc4efbe913c960c4ba89bdd0aa23a3e","tid":1299790,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e176c3564edd99a6bc98db1e3422caf466f3d91","tid":1299790,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"重申7大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>承諾不推行社會信用評分制度</strong></span><br />\n7.<strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">拆除所有監控燈柱</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試著說監控燈柱, 不要說智慧燈柱</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32fd68ea5d7fe7de078c226506603b4034c4c72","tid":1299790,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u6Lb70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u6Lb70.png&h=84e8e474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14/7 已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih